    <published>2017-02-13T02:47:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-03-28T15:04:02.936Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://wxblog.b0.upaiyun.com/pic/post/2017-02-13/Network-945x349.png" alt=""><br>Dnsmasq适用于小型网络架构，为其中的主机提供DNS、DHCP等服务。本文将介绍其DNS功能的简单使用，并在内网环境中搭建Dnsmasq服务器为两个节点提供DNS服务。<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h2 id="Dnsmasq-简介和适用平台"><a href="#Dnsmasq-简介和适用平台" class="headerlink" title="Dnsmasq 简介和适用平台"></a>Dnsmasq 简介和适用平台</h2><blockquote>
<p>Dnsmasq provides network infrastructure for small networks: DNS, DHCP, router advertisement and network boot. It is designed to be lightweight and have a small footprint, suitable for resource constrained routers and firewalls. It has also been widely used for tethering on smartphones and portable hotspots, and to support virtual networking in virtualisation frameworks.<br>Supported platforms include Linux (with glibc and uclibc), Android, *BSD, and Mac OS X. Dnsmasq is included in most Linux distributions and the ports systems of FreeBSD, OpenBSD and NetBSD. Dnsmasq provides full IPv6 support.<br><a href="http://www.thekelleys.org.uk/dnsmasq/doc.html" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">摘自Dnsmasq官网</a></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="Dnsmasq-部署"><a href="#Dnsmasq-部署" class="headerlink" title="Dnsmasq 部署"></a>Dnsmasq 部署</h2><table>
